{"id":791688,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Chapman_(cinematographer)","text":"Michael Crawford Chapman, A.S.C. (November 21, 1935 \u2013 September 20, 2020) was an American cinematographer and movie director. He was known for his works with Martin Scorsese and Ivan Reitman. Chapman was born in New York City. His best known works was in \"Taxi Driver\", \"Raging Bull\", \"Space Jam\" and in \"The Fugitive\".\nChapman died from congestive heart failure on September 20, 2020, at his home in Los Angeles, aged 84.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"American_Society_of_Cinematographers","surface_form":"A.S.C.","offset":26},{"uri":"Cinematographer","surface_form":"cinematographer","offset":90},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":110},{"uri":"Martin_Scorsese","surface_form":"Martin Scorsese","offset":158},{"uri":"Ivan_Reitman","surface_form":"Ivan Reitman","offset":178},{"uri":"New_York_City","surface_form":"New York City","offset":212},{"uri":"Taxi_Driver","surface_form":"Taxi Driver","offset":256},{"uri":"Raging_Bull","surface_form":"Raging Bull","offset":271},{"uri":"Space_Jam","surface_form":"Space Jam","offset":286},{"uri":"The_Fugitive_(1993_movie)","surface_form":"The Fugitive","offset":305},{"uri":"Congestive_heart_failure","surface_form":"congestive heart failure","offset":338},{"uri":"Los_Angeles","surface_form":"Los Angeles","offset":401}]}